# Realm Battles Game

## Description
Realm Battles is an online strategy game where players can engage in battles, manage resources, and develop their technologies. Players build units, upgrade technologies, and compete against other users in a vast universe.

## Features
- User registration and login system
- Dynamic game mechanics with unit production and management
- Technologies and upgrades
- Real-time resource tracking 

## Installation
To run this project locally, clone the repository and run the PHP server:

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone <repository-link>
   cd <repository-folder>